  // ====================================================== HELP TEXT
  var HELP_MAIN = 'Welcome to <b>Story Studio</b>! In 5 steps:<br><br>1️⃣ <b>Pick a story</b> from the list.<br>2️⃣ <b>Describe your character</b> (look, hair, etc.).<br>3️⃣ <b>Re-balance the sections</b> — make parts longer or shorter.<br>4️⃣ <b>Open any section</b> to tweak its mood, positions and details.<br>5️⃣ <b>Export</b> and send the file to the creator — they’ll generate your images.<br><br>Everything auto-saves in your browser, so you can come back later. Look for the <b>?</b> next to anything you’re unsure about.';
