  var HELP_MOODS = 'These are the facial expressions / emotions used in this part. Use the “+ Add a mood” button to add more. “Use the story’s moods” keeps the variety the creator designed; “Choose my own moods” lets you add and remove; “Force one mood” uses a single expression the whole part.';
